{"type":"message","id":"c0434de6","parentId":"9e075499","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:30:00.910Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:321d856c-eb47-44d0-a1de-24fd64d31f4f 盘后复盘-脚本化] 运行盘后复盘脚本：1)检查交易日(休市日:20260101 20260102 20260216-20260220 20260223 20260406 20260501 20260504 20260505 20260619 20260925 20261001-20261007) 2)运行 cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace-chairong && uv run python scripts/postmarket_pipeline.py 3)输出结果摘要\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 — 18:30 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-14 10:30 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776162600908}}
{"type":"message","id":"ddf84386","parentId":"c0434de6","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:30:34.546Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nThis is a cron job execution request for a post-market analysis script. The user wants me to:\n\n1. Check if today is a trading day (market closed on: 20260101 20260102 20260216-20260220 20260223 20260406 20260501 20260504 20260505 20260619 20260925 20261001-20261007)\n2. Run the post-market pipeline script\n3. Output results summary\n\nLet me first check if today is a trading day. Today is 2026-04-14 (Tuesday, April 14th, 2026).\n\nLooking at the market closure dates:\n- 20260101, 20260102 (January 1-2, 2026)\n- 20260216-20260220 (February 16-20, 2026) \n- 20260223 (February 23, 2026)\n- 20260406 (April 6, 2026)\n- 20260501, 20260504, 20260505 (May 1, 4-5, 2026)\n- 20260619 (June 19, 2026)\n- 20260925 (September 25, 2026)\n- 20261001-20261007 (October 1-7, 2026)\n\nToday (2026-04-14) is NOT in the closure list, so it's a trading day.\n\nNow I need to run the post-market pipeline script at /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace-chairong/scripts/postmarket_pipeline.py using uv run python.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n<thinking>\nI need to execute the post-market analysis pipeline. First, let me check if today is a trading day by examining the market closure dates, then run the script.\n\nCurrent date: 2026-04-14\nMarket closure dates provided: 20260101, 20260102, 20260216-20260220, 20260223, 20260406, 20260501, 20260504, 20260505, 20260619, 20260925, 20261001-20261007\n\nToday (2026-04-14) is not in the closure list, so it's a trading day. Now I'll run the post-market pipeline script.\n</thinking>\n\nI'll execute the post-market analysis pipeline. First, let me verify today is a trading day and then run the script.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_becf4f2a292c47bb8d0a83a4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace-chairong && uv run pyth